ile: \"/Library/Python/2.7/site-packages/grpc/early_adopter/implementations.py\", line 161, in **exit**\n  self._rear_link.stop()\nFile: \"/Library/Python/2.7/site-packages/grpc/_adapter/rear.py\", line 373, in stop\n  self._stop()\nFile: \"/Library/Python/2.7/site-packages/grpc/_adapter/rear.py\", line 356, in _stop\n  self._condition.wait()\nFile: \"/System/Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/2.7/lib/python2.7/threading.py\", line 339, in wait\n  waiter.acquire()\n"
